FBIS3-18209 "drweu040aa_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 March 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Italy: Action `In Line' With Resolution LD2802131494 Rome RAI Due Television Network in Italian 1200 GMT 28 Feb 94 LD2802131494 Rome RAI Due Television Network Language: Italian Article Type:BFN [Text] It is a sad thing, but it is in line with the UN resolution on the no-fly zone in Bosnia, Italy's Defense Minister Fabio Fabbri said on the downing of the Serbian planes. The international community and the UN cannot help using force if they want to be credible when they say they want to guarantee world order and security, Fabbri said.
